[
  {
    "startTime": 6.96,
    "endTime": 9.243,
    "text": "Rob: Hello, and welcome to 6 Minute"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.243,
    "endTime": 11.512,
    "text": "English from BBC Learning English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.512,
    "endTime": 12.179,
    "text": "I'm Rob..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.179,
    "endTime": 13.179,
    "text": "Georgina: And I'm Georgina."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.179,
    "endTime": 15.499,
    "text": "Rob: Now, Georgina, how resilient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.499,
    "endTime": 17.25,
    "text": "are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.25,
    "endTime": 19.531,
    "text": "Georgina: Resilient? You mean able to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.531,
    "endTime": 21.482,
    "text": "cope with difficult situations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.483,
    "endTime": 22.490000000000002,
    "text": "I have a pile of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.49,
    "endTime": 24.848,
    "text": "work to do today, but I'm remaining"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.848,
    "endTime": 26.869,
    "text": "calm and not getting stressed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.869,
    "endTime": 28.659,
    "text": "Rob: That's good, you are showing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.659,
    "endTime": 30.148,
    "text": "resilience. And today we're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.149,
    "endTime": 31.75,
    "text": "discussing whether we're born"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.75,
    "endTime": 34.15,
    "text": "with resilience or we have to learn it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.15,
    "endTime": 36.26,
    "text": "Georgina: OK, Rob. But first I expect you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.26,
    "endTime": 38.86,
    "text": "going to ask me a question - bring it on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.86,
    "endTime": 41.76,
    "text": "Rob: OK. Resilience is also a word used in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.76,
    "endTime": 44.47,
    "text": "science to describe the characteristic of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.47,
    "endTime": 46.26,
    "text": "a substance or object."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.26,
    "endTime": 47.68,
    "text": "But what does it mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.698,
    "endTime": 50.289,
    "text": "a) That it's is very tough or hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.289,
    "endTime": 52.547000000000004,
    "text": "b) That it can return to its original"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.547,
    "endTime": 53.949,
    "text": "shape after being bent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.95,
    "endTime": 56.120000000000005,
    "text": "c) It can turn from a solid into"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.12,
    "endTime": 57.54,
    "text": "a liquid quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.54,
    "endTime": 59.66,
    "text": "Georgina: I have a feeling it means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.662,
    "endTime": 61.813,
    "text": "b) an object that returns to its"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.813,
    "endTime": 63.2,
    "text": "original shape after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.2,
    "endTime": 64.2,
    "text": "being bent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.2,
    "endTime": 66.39,
    "text": "Rob: OK, I'll let you know if you were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.39,
    "endTime": 68.507,
    "text": "correct at the end of the programme."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.507,
    "endTime": 69.33,
    "text": "But let's talk"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.33,
    "endTime": 71.399,
    "text": "more about human resilience. There are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.4,
    "endTime": 73.2,
    "text": "many self-help books and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.2,
    "endTime": 74.5,
    "text": "motivational speakers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.5,
    "endTime": 76.44,
    "text": "all promising us we can learn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.44,
    "endTime": 77.86,
    "text": "to be resilient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.86,
    "endTime": 79.76,
    "text": "Georgina: Well, it is a useful trait to have,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.766,
    "endTime": 81.97,
    "text": "and it's something that can help you deal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.97,
    "endTime": 84.539,
    "text": "with many difficult situations from coping"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.54,
    "endTime": 87.11,
    "text": "with the pressures of work to handling the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.11,
    "endTime": 88.46,
    "text": "death of a loved one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.46,
    "endTime": 90.03899999999999,
    "text": "Rob: And it's more than just telling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.04,
    "endTime": 92.5,
    "text": "someone to 'toughen up' or 'get a grip',"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 94.16,
    "text": "as Dr David Westley knows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.16,
    "endTime": 95.899,
    "text": "He is Head of Psychology at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.9,
    "endTime": 97.97,
    "text": "Middlesex University and talked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.97,
    "endTime": 99.74,
    "text": "about levels of resilience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.74,
    "endTime": 100.8,
    "text": "on the BBC World Service"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.8,
    "endTime": 102.84,
    "text": "programme, The Why Factor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.56,
    "endTime": 105.24000000000001,
    "text": "Dr David Westley: First of all, there's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.24,
    "endTime": 108.24,
    "text": "our social supports, our communities,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.24,
    "endTime": 109.78,
    "text": "our families, the people who are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.78,
    "endTime": 111.255,
    "text": "important to us, the organisations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.26,
    "endTime": 113.10000000000001,
    "text": "we work for, so one way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.1,
    "endTime": 114.44,
    "text": "we can look at resilience is to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.44,
    "endTime": 116.39,
    "text": "measure that - the amount of social"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.391,
    "endTime": 117.956,
    "text": "support available to us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.956,
    "endTime": 119.26,
    "text": "Another way to think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.26,
    "endTime": 121.52000000000001,
    "text": "about resilience is to think about how we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.52,
    "endTime": 124.539,
    "text": "think about the situations we are in. So,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.54,
    "endTime": 126.2,
    "text": "for example, one way to look at that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.2,
    "endTime": 127.4,
    "text": "would be just to look at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.4,
    "endTime": 128.78,
    "text": "how optimistic people are as a guide"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.788,
    "endTime": 131.579,
    "text": "to how resilient they might be when times"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.593,
    "endTime": 133.85,
    "text": "get tough. And then a third level"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.85,
    "endTime": 135.768,
    "text": "that we can look at for resilience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.768,
    "endTime": 138.005,
    "text": "is a biological level - how well we can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.005,
    "endTime": 139.21,
    "text": "soothe ourselves, calm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.21,
    "endTime": 141.708,
    "text": "ourselves down, how well we can actually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.708,
    "endTime": 144.32,
    "text": "regulate our own nervous systems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.34,
    "endTime": 146.42000000000002,
    "text": "at times of distress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.16,
    "endTime": 148.82,
    "text": "Georgina: Right, so Dr Westley describes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.82,
    "endTime": 151.28,
    "text": "social supports - the people around"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.285,
    "endTime": 152.2,
    "text": "us who we can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.2,
    "endTime": 154.76,
    "text": "talk to and support us and generally make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.76,
    "endTime": 157.62,
    "text": "us feel better. I think he's saying, with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.62,
    "endTime": 160.74,
    "text": "more support we'll feel more resilient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.74,
    "endTime": 163.24,
    "text": "Rob: It's interesting to note that a resilient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.243,
    "endTime": 164.686,
    "text": "person isn't necessarily"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.687,
    "endTime": 165.78,
    "text": "someone quiet, who doesn't make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.78,
    "endTime": 167.7,
    "text": "a fuss and gets on with things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.7,
    "endTime": 169.95899999999997,
    "text": "Some experts think it's people who ask"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.96,
    "endTime": 171.96,
    "text": "for help and use this social support"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.96,
    "endTime": 173.94,
    "text": "network who are acting in a more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.94,
    "endTime": 174.92,
    "text": "resilient way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.92,
    "endTime": 177.17899999999997,
    "text": "Georgina: It's a good point. And another"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.18,
    "endTime": 178.74,
    "text": "level of resilience is how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.74,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "optimistic someone is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 182.88,
    "text": "Being optimistic means having positive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.88,
    "endTime": 184.313,
    "text": "thoughts about the future and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.313,
    "endTime": 185.35,
    "text": "believing things will"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.35,
    "endTime": 188.094,
    "text": "turn out well. A positive mind means you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.094,
    "endTime": 191.18,
    "text": "can deal with situations that, at first, look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.18,
    "endTime": 193.255,
    "text": "tough. Another level Dr Westley"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.26,
    "endTime": 195.72,
    "text": "mentioned was our biological level -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.72,
    "endTime": 198.7,
    "text": "how our bodies cope in times of distress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.7,
    "endTime": 200.339,
    "text": "Distress is the feeling you get"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.34,
    "endTime": 202.04,
    "text": "when you are worried or upset"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.04,
    "endTime": 203.1,
    "text": "by something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.1,
    "endTime": 205.239,
    "text": "Rob: So, when we're distressed, a resilient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.24,
    "endTime": 207.02,
    "text": "person is able to soothe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.02,
    "endTime": 209.20000000000002,
    "text": "his or her body and regulate his or her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.2,
    "endTime": 210.64,
    "text": "nervous system, which"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.64,
    "endTime": 212.42,
    "text": "helps them stay calm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.42,
    "endTime": 214.339,
    "text": "Georgina: But, Rob, the big question is,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.34,
    "endTime": 216.18,
    "text": "are we born with resilience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.18,
    "endTime": 217.42000000000002,
    "text": "or can we learn it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.42,
    "endTime": 219.38,
    "text": "Experts speaking on The Why Factor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.38,
    "endTime": 221.12,
    "text": "programme tended to think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.12,
    "endTime": 222.20000000000002,
    "text": "it could be learned."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.2,
    "endTime": 224.333,
    "text": "Rob: Yes, one of them is Ann Masten,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.334,
    "endTime": 226.263,
    "text": "a professor at the University of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.263,
    "endTime": 227.95000000000002,
    "text": "Minnesota. From her studies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.95,
    "endTime": 229.57899999999998,
    "text": "she found it was something that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.58,
    "endTime": 231.18,
    "text": "we learn when we need to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.18,
    "endTime": 232.96,
    "text": "Georgina: Ann Masten talks about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.969,
    "endTime": 235.018,
    "text": "how some of the children she studied"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.018,
    "endTime": 236.099,
    "text": "manifest resilience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.099,
    "endTime": 237.433,
    "text": "from the start. When"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.433,
    "endTime": 239.94,
    "text": "something manifests, it shows clearly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.94,
    "endTime": 241.77,
    "text": "and is easy to notice. They"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.77,
    "endTime": 244.12300000000002,
    "text": "remain resilient despite adversity - a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.123,
    "endTime": 245.88,
    "text": "difficult time in their life that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.9,
    "endTime": 247.54,
    "text": "they've had to face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.54,
    "endTime": 249.57899999999998,
    "text": "Rob: Other children, what she calls the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.58,
    "endTime": 251.4,
    "text": "late bloomers, started off"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.4,
    "endTime": 253.34,
    "text": "less resilient, struggled"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.34,
    "endTime": 255.24,
    "text": "with adversity, but turned their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.24,
    "endTime": 257.495,
    "text": "lives around by becoming more resilient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.495,
    "endTime": 258.54,
    "text": "Maybe we can learn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.54,
    "endTime": 259.56,
    "text": "resilience from a having"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.56,
    "endTime": 260.76,
    "text": "a bad experience?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.76,
    "endTime": 262.4,
    "text": "Georgina: Well, one thing Ann went on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.4,
    "endTime": 263.919,
    "text": "to say was that families and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.92,
    "endTime": 265.14000000000004,
    "text": "friends can be a great"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.14,
    "endTime": 267.02,
    "text": "support and help with resilience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.021,
    "endTime": 269.098,
    "text": "Those that were 'late bloomers' only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.1,
    "endTime": 270.31,
    "text": "connected with adults"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.31,
    "endTime": 272.38,
    "text": "and mentors later in life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.38,
    "endTime": 274.02,
    "text": "Rob: Yes, she says that teachers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.02,
    "endTime": 275.84,
    "text": "or parents are role models in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.84,
    "endTime": 277.719,
    "text": "how to handle adversity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.72,
    "endTime": 279.46000000000004,
    "text": "And children are watching; they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.47,
    "endTime": 280.86,
    "text": "learning from the adults around"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.874,
    "endTime": 281.69,
    "text": "them by seeing how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.69,
    "endTime": 283.6,
    "text": "they react when they get challenged"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.6,
    "endTime": 284.88,
    "text": "by something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.52,
    "endTime": 287.68,
    "text": "Time now to find out how resilient you are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.69,
    "endTime": 289.78,
    "text": "when you discover the correct answer to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.795,
    "endTime": 291.39000000000004,
    "text": "the question I asked earlier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.39,
    "endTime": 292.71,
    "text": "I said that 'resilience'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.71,
    "endTime": 295.479,
    "text": "is also a word used in science to describe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.48,
    "endTime": 296.74,
    "text": "the characteristic of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.74,
    "endTime": 298.68,
    "text": "a substance or object."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.68,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "But what does that mean? Is it..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.0,
    "endTime": 302.3,
    "text": "a) It is very tough or hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.3,
    "endTime": 304.995,
    "text": "b) It can return to its original shape"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.995,
    "endTime": 306.2,
    "text": "after being bent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.2,
    "endTime": 308.013,
    "text": "c) It can turn from a solid"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.013,
    "endTime": 309.489,
    "text": "into a liquid quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.49,
    "endTime": 311.19,
    "text": "And what did you say, Georgina?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.19,
    "endTime": 313.754,
    "text": "Georgina: I said it was b) It can return to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.754,
    "endTime": 315.90000000000003,
    "text": "its original shape after being bent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.9,
    "endTime": 318.126,
    "text": "Rob: And you are right - well done!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.127,
    "endTime": 319.68,
    "text": "Bamboo is a good example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.68,
    "endTime": 322.0,
    "text": "of a resilient material - you can bend it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.0,
    "endTime": 323.82,
    "text": "it doesn't break and returns"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.82,
    "endTime": 325.08,
    "text": "to its original shape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.08,
    "endTime": 326.639,
    "text": "Georgina: Thanks for the science lesson,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.639,
    "endTime": 327.987,
    "text": "Rob. Now we need to recap the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.987,
    "endTime": 328.73,
    "text": "vocabulary we've"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.73,
    "endTime": 329.73,
    "text": "mentioned today..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.73,
    "endTime": 331.63,
    "text": "Rob: Yes, we've talked about being"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.63,
    "endTime": 333.223,
    "text": "resilient, an adjective that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.223,
    "endTime": 334.76,
    "text": "describes someone's ability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.76,
    "endTime": 337.01,
    "text": "to cope with difficult situations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.02,
    "endTime": 339.919,
    "text": "When you do this you show resilience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.92,
    "endTime": 341.353,
    "text": "Georgina: Someone who is optimistic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.353,
    "endTime": 342.839,
    "text": "has positive thoughts about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.84,
    "endTime": 344.489,
    "text": "the future and believes things"
